{"article_id":"QR3ZUqWCNumG1ETl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"In this White House , no one knows when the ax will fall","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"or who will be swinging it .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"A new day of firing and fury","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"culminating in a staggering power play by first lady Melania Trump","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"deepened already historic dysfunction in the administration on Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"leaving top officials blindsided and confused .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Even compared with the senior staff knifings , bureaucratic turmoil and raging chaos","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that passes for normality in President Donald Trump 's White House ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"her sudden move against a top foreign policy official was a bombshell .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"In a public statement","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that came out of nowhere ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"the first lady 's office warned","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that deputy national security adviser Mira Ricardel ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"with whom she reportedly clashed over a recent Africa trip ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"`` no longer deserves the honor","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"of serving in this White House . ''","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Her dramatic intervention sparked speculation","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"that the first lady was at odds with her husband ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"was overstepping her role","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and that the East Wing was going rogue .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Melania Trump had already said in an ABC interview last month","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that she did n't trust some White House staffers .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Now , she was doing something about it .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"One person told CNN","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that , incredibly , Trump , chief of staff John Kelly and White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders had no idea","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"the statement was coming .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"A source told CNN 's Jeff Zeleny","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that Trump","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"-- who often finds it difficult to fire people in person","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"despite his schtick on NBC 's `` The Apprentice '' --","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"had decided","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"that Ricardel has to go ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"though she was being given time","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"to clear her desk .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"as is often the case in this poorly run White House ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"there was uncertainty at first over Ricardel 's actual fate .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"It was not clear on Wednesday morning","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"whether she had been officially dismissed ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"whether she would show up for work as usual","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"or if she might be found a spot elsewhere in the administration .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"Later Wednesday , Sanders issued a statement","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"confirming","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Ricardel will leave her White House position ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"while noting","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that Ricardel will `` transition to a new role within the Administration . ''","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"It 's not unusual for unease to stalk the White House after a midterm election loss ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"as staffers","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"exhausted by the first half of the President 's mandate","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"give way to fresher troops .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"And Tuesday was not the first time","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"a first lady has leaned on her husband over a staffer","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"she finds irksome .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"But this President 's mercurial temperament and the nest of vipers","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"that is his West Wing","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"has inflicted more nerve-rattling pressure on his staff","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"than is normal even in the White House ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"where crises are always just around the corner .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"The current turbulence and sense of presidential norms","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"being shattered by an emotional and erratic president","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"feels different and more consequential than the wild staff intrigues of early in the presidency .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"It 's beginning to raise real questions","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"about what is in store for the nation over the second half of Trump 's term .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Several Cabinet members","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"-- including Homeland Security Secretary Kirstjen Nielsen --","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"are being targeted by whispering campaigns , leaks and speculation about their fates","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"as trial balloons float about possible replacements .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Kelly ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"who has survived several rounds of scuttlebutt about his often supposedly imminent departure ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"is said to be heading for the exit again .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"And leaked reports","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that Trump sees Ryan Zinke as vulnerable to Democratic oversight","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"have weakened the Interior secretary 's position .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Trump is meanwhile digging in on his constitutionally questionable appointment of Matthew Whitaker , a critic of Robert Mueller ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"to oversee the special counsel probe as acting attorney general","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"after Jeff Sessions was fired .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Sanders had been expected to leave , along with her deputy Raj Shah ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"but their status remains uncertain .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Trump uses pandemonium as an instrument of personal power ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"leaving everyone off balance and unsure of what will happen next ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"while he sits in the center of the storm","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"ready to make his next move .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Sowing disruption in Washington ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"while confounding the political establishment and perceptions","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"of how a White House should be run ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"allows the President to keep faith with his political base .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"So palace intrigue has been part of the administration from the start , along with media narratives","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that Trump is running his White House like a reality show","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"and is constantly firing off distractions","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"for reporters to chase .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"It seems certain that Trump will emerge from this highly charged moment with fewer constraints","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"if senior staffers","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"who have tried to keep him within the bounds of presidential custom and the law","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"depart .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"He may have more latitude","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"to follow an unpredictable course","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"in which he sometimes seems to brush up against governing conventions and constitutional guardrails","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"he often does n't seem to even know","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"are there .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"This could be an increasing problem","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"when the administration faces a sudden burst of investigations from the new Democratic House , a reality","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"for which lax oversight by Republicans has left it deeply underprepared .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"JUST WATCHED WH aide to exit","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"after Melania pushed for ouster","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"MUST WATCH WH aide to exit","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"after Melania pushed for ouster","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"01:35","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"And there is a good chance","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"that Trump becomes even more distracted by the Mueller investigation","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"with speculation heating up about possible new indictments and the contents of the special counsel 's long awaited final report .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"On Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"with his White House in uproar ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"he was sitting down with his lawyers","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"to answer written questions","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"posed by Mueller","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"-- a potential critical moment for his presidency .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Amazingly , the President is yet to face a major international crisis","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that he did not precipitate","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"- like a close military call with a major adversary or a financial crash ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"that will require focused , unambiguous leadership and a crack team","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"operating with unity and purpose .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"That seems an unlikely prospect in this White House .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"There must also be questions ,","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"given the ever more fractious nature of life in his administration ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"whether top-level staffers on the GOP bench","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"who might be persuaded to serve","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"are going to have second thoughts .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"After all , officials like Nielsen and Kelly have put their own reputations on the line ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"defending the President 's controversial policies on immigration ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"only for him to turn on them in the end .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Right now , the only White House staffers","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"who might consider themselves safe","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"are his kin :","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"his daughter Ivanka and son-in-law Jared Kushner .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"But the danger","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"of running a West Wing on the nepotistic model of Trump 's business","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"has been made clear recently with the crisis over the killing of Saudi journalist Jamal Khashoggi .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"The assassination ,","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"which caused global outrage ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"is being widely blamed on Mohammad bin Salman , the Crown Prince","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"on whom Kushner","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"-- going around the State Department --","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"anchored Middle East policy .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"Tuesday 's swoop by the first lady was remarkable .","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"In a show of force","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"apparently brewing for days ,","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"she made Ricardel 's position untenable .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"In a dash of added intrigue , Melania Trump twisted the knife with national security adviser John Bolton ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"who has forged his own deserved reputation as a ruthless bureaucratic assassin ,","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"out of the action","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"-- nearly 10,000 miles away in Singapore .","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"It was not the first time","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"a senior West Wing staffer paid the price","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"for falling out with a first lady .","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"Gossip often bubbled over ill will between Nancy Reagan and ex-White House chief of staff Don Regan .","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"George Stephanopoulos wrote in his memoir about clashes with Hillary Clinton","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"when he served in her husband 's White House .","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"And there was often talk of tension between Michelle Obama and her husband 's first press secretary , Robert Gibbs .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"But it 's hard to find a precedent for the public , categorical , felling of Ricardel by Melania Trump , a strike","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"that exemplified the first lady 's willingness","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"to throw around her political weight .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"Still , Marc Short , Trump 's former congressional liaison , told CNN 's Erin Burnett","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"while her move was unprecedented ,","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"it was not likely to start a new trend .","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"`` I think","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"you will find out over time","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"that this is probably an exception","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"and that the first lady probably had reasons , ''","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"Some White House sources painted a picture of Ricardel as tough to work with","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"she had picked a lot of fights","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"since coming aboard in April .","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"`` She 'd run through a brick wall for you","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"but her personality is n't for everyone , ''","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"said another official .","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"Still , Ricardel has not yet had the chance","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"to tell her own story .","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"And the tone of any White House is set from the top","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"-- and there is no doubt","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"that there are few tougher places","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"to work in America .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":369,"left":0,"right":368,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":368,"left":230,"right":367,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":186,"right":229,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":229,"left":192,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":189,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":188,"right":6,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":187,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":187,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":190,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":190,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":202,"right":227,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":198,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":194,"right":197,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":193,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":193,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":195,"right":196,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":195,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":17,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":18,"right":199,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":227,"left":204,"right":226,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"p